plot: The next generation of the students at Degrassi are here. Degrassi: The Next Generation takes place 14 years after the cult hit show &"Degrassi Junior High&" as students continue to deal with the obstacles of being a teenager. From issues like relationship problems, homosexuality and bullying to more darker issues like rape, school shooting and death. Degrassi: The Next Generation plunges into the world of what this generation is really going through.   Written by  devil_730
